{"tid":1748736,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記得梁凌杰嗎？","createTime":"2019-11-23T21:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T22:52:03.000Z","uid":126099,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"505edc2af2ea848f8ca34089e8908901074c9d30","tid":1748736,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:20:28.000Z","msg":"梁凌杰（英語：Marco Leung，1984年3月7日－2019年6月15日），香港社運人士，曾參與雨傘革命與2019年6月9日反對逃犯條例修訂草案遊行。在6月16日遊行前夕，在金鐘太古廣場高位掛上標語示威，後從高處墮下，經搶救後不治，得年35歲[2]。<br />\n<br />\n梁凌杰生前單身，與父母同住。其家中亦有姊妹[2]。<br />\n<br />\n他曾於2014年參加雨傘革命，主要駐守旺角佔領區，外號「化骨龍」[3][4]。<span style=\"color: red;\">在2016年香港立法會選舉中，梁凌杰曾為工聯會郭偉強助選[5]。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/梁凌杰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E6%9D%B0&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FhQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=18141e04\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/梁凌杰</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">仲講緊投白票嘅你，對唔對得住梁義士？</span>"},{"pid":"1ac8bff76677e6b8e9025b31efb7c03ac4761edf","tid":1748736,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:21:28.000Z","msg":"紅色字想帶出？"},{"pid":"5616ff41246b4e826b9389fc2430e962bdce4dc9","tid":1748736,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/ff/Man_protesting_Hong_Kong%27s_extradition_law_in_Pacific_Place_20190615.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Ff%2Fff%2FMan_protesting_Hong_Kong%2527s_extradition_law_in_Pacific_Place_20190615.png&h=459e145f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身穿黃色雨衣的梁凌杰在太古廣場高位危站"},{"pid":"6d9ef21c3a9cfeb31f75d70cd98068f426cfcaf7","tid":1748736,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ac8bff76677e6b8e9025b31efb7c03ac4761edf","tid":1748736,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:21:28.000Z","msg":"紅色字想帶出？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:25:56.000Z","msg":"當初我唔知梁義士點解會幫工聯會拉票<br />\n但梁義士嘅死都係多得工聯會強推送中<br />\n求下大家，唔可以比保皇黨贏"},{"pid":"d1df92c4e4e2d0dcd4ae30e6667fd0e1055dc822","tid":1748736,"uid":126099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:30:50.000Z","msg":"感謝社會各界人士悼念杰仔。每一位善良熱心的香港人，包括兒子在內，都希望香港能變得更好，讓每人都能安居樂業、自由發聲；而每一位勇敢地走上街頭市民都是因為深愛香港。年輕人要好好保全自己，活下去，才能繼續為社會不公不義之事勇於發聲[26][29]。\t&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&thinsp;梁凌杰父母"},{"pid":"7de86090ed4564dd77869629a87520b121d3f02f","tid":1748736,"uid":201170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T22:49:48.000Z","msg":"Blocked 88"},{"pid":"23bce0e3092e5e570fe17387583e759371cfa3c0","tid":1748736,"uid":6142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T22:52:03.000Z","msg":"點會忘記。。"}]}